==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Untold
<hw>Un*told"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not told;
not related; not revealed; <as>as, <ex>untold</ex>
secrets</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not numbered or counted; <as>as, <ex>untold</ex>
money</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Untolerable</ent>⟦br⟧
